        <mxCell id="summary_text" value="Internal Flow Sequence:&#xa;1. Extract signatures from source → 2. Map parameters to fuzzer types&#xa;3. Select appropriate template → 4. Generate harness code&#xa;5. Compile with sanitizers → 6. Generate build scripts → 7. Package deliverables&#xa;&#xa;Key Decision Points:&#xa;• Signature extraction enables type-aware fuzzing&#xa;• Template selection based on bug class and harness type&#xa;• Sanitizer selection from fuzz plan metadata&#xa;• Parallel generation of build scripts and compilation" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="930" y="1430" width="780" height="80" as="geometry"/>
